commentary: Haris Sohail to McCullum, OUT superb catch by Younis at extra cover! And Haris keeps increasing his tally of wickets. Nathan wanted to slog it over midwicket, the bat turns in his hands and the leading edge lobs towards extra cover.. Younis was at cover, but makes a quick move towards his right to catch it on a full stretch
